title: Dr. Long Name
description:
Written by Zack Phillips
Starring Dan Hodapp, Jonathan Marballi, Kerry O'Brien, Langan Kingsley, Lisa Kleinman, Avery Monsen

Directed by Jim Santangeli

Graphics by Avery Monsen.

From Maude Night at the Upright Citizens Brigade Theatre, April 1, 2013.

Filmed by Kevin Mead and Yoni Lotan
Edited by Kevin Mead
